15 WHEREAS, veterans embody the spirit of service and willingness to find meaning in
16 something greater than themselves, and it is abundantly fitting and proper that the
17 outstanding accomplishments and sacrifices of these remarkable and distinguished
18 Americans be honored appropriately.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED AND ENACTED BY THE GENERAL
20 ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA that the entire portion of State Route 10/State
21 Route 154/Memorial Drive in Fulton and DeKalb counties is dedicated as the Veterans
22 Memorial Drive.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Department of Transportation is authorized and
24 directed to erect and maintain appropriate signs dedicating the Veterans Memorial Drive.
25 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
26 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
27 Department of Transportation.
